OL,3,CCompensation for blind man who fell
OL,4,Conto train tracks
OL,6,FA blind student who fell onto train
OL,7,Ftracks at Manchester Piccadilly
OL,8,Frailway station after an assistance
OL,9,Fservice failed to meet him has secured
OL,10,F#18,000 in compensation.
OL,12,F23-year-old Abdul Eneser injured his
OL,13,Fknees, hands and neck and suffers from
OL,14,Fongoing anxiety after the incident in
OL,15,FMay 2022, law firm Leigh Day said.
OL,17,FThe law student had booked Passenger
OL,18,FAssist in advance but arrived by train
OL,19,Fat the station on a later service than
OL,20,Fplanned after missing a connection at
OL,21,FPreston because of delays.
