OL,3,CCompensation for blind man who fell
OL,4,Conto train tracks
OL,6,FAvanti West Coast staff at Preston
OL,7,Ftold him they would radio through to
OL,8,FManchester Piccadilly to tell them he
OL,9,Fwas on the train, but when he arrived
OL,10,Fafter midnight there was no-one there
OL,11,Fto meet him.
OL,13,FHe was later told all Passenger Assist
OL,14,Fstaff had gone home.
OL,16,FMr Abdul tried to find the steps to
OL,17,Fleave the station but fell onto the
OL,18,Ftracks.
