OL,6,FHe managed to pull himself back onto
OL,7,Fthe platform one minute before a non-
OL,8,Fstop freight train passed through on
OL,9,Fthe same tracks, Leigh Day said.
OL,11,FThe law firm launched court
OL,12,Fproceedings against Network Rail under
OL,13,Fthe 2010 Equality Act and the
OL,14,FOccupiers Liability Act 1957, for
OL,15,Ffailing to install tactile paving at
OL,16,Fthe station.
