OL,6,FThis paving is used to warn blind and
OL,7,Fvisually impaired people they are
OL,8,Fapproaching a hazard such as a
OL,9,Fplatform edge, often by using raised
OL,10,Fstuds.
OL,12,FNetwork Rail did not admit liability
OL,13,Fbut agreed to pay Mr Abdul
OL,14,Fcompensation, according to Leigh Day.
OL,16,FThe Press Association understands the
OL,17,Famount was #18,000. This was first
OL,18,Freported by the Guardian.
