OL,6,FLeigh Day senior associate solicitor
OL,7,FKate Egerton said: "Network Rail and
OL,8,Ftrain operators have a clear
OL,9,Fobligation to ensure that train
OL,10,Fstations are accessible for all.
OL,12,F"Not only is it distressing for
OL,13,Fpassengers with visual impairments to
OL,14,Ftry to navigate inaccessible platforms
OL,15,Fand services, it is also extremely
OL,16,Fdangerous.
