OL,4,Conto train tracks
OL,6,F"Whilst I am pleased that we were able
OL,7,Fto secure this settlement for Abdul,
OL,8,Fhis case and continued experiences
OL,9,Fhighlight wider accessibility issues
OL,10,Facross the rail network that need to
OL,11,Fbe addressed."
OL,13,FA Network Rail spokesperson said: "We
OL,14,Fare extremely sorry for the experience
OL,15,FAbdul Eneser suffered at Manchester
OL,16,FPiccadilly. We let him down and have
OL,17,Foffered him our full and unreserved
OL,18,Fapology.
