OL,6,F"We recognise that there is much to do
OL,7,Fto make the railway more accessible
OL,8,Ffor all and are working closely with
OL,9,Findustry partners to deliver these
OL,10,Fimprovements across the rail network
OL,11,Fas quickly as we can."
OL,13,FIn July last year, the Department for
OL,14,FTransport said the roll out of tactile
OL,15,Fpaving across all railway stations in
OL,16,FBritain had been completed.
